These SVG mimetype icons are sourced from the GNOME Adwaita Icon Theme
(https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/adwaita-icon-theme) and are redistributed
under their original license (CC-BY-SA 3.0 / LGPL, see Adwaita's COPYING).

They are vendored here so the built-in SFTP file manager renders consistent
file-type icons across all installations (including Flatpak sandboxes and
distributions that do not ship the Adwaita scalable mimetypes).
